        <briefdescription>
<para>Runs a limited self-test on the driver/device. </para>        </briefdescription>
        <detaileddescription>
<para>This test does a read/write test of the Interrupt Registers There is no loopback capabilities for the device such that this test does not send or receive data.</para><para><parameterlist kind="param"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>InstancePtr</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>is a pointer to the <ref refid="struct_x_iic" kindref="compound">XIic</ref> instance to be worked on.</para></parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="return"><para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>XST_SUCCESS if no errors are found</para></listitem><listitem><para>XST_FAILURE if errors are found</para></listitem></itemizedlist>
</para></simplesect>
<simplesect kind="note"><para>None. </para></simplesect>
</para>        </detaileddescription>
